02:20.560 --> 02:22.100
Cepat.

02:27.150 --> 02:27.630
Yan.

02:27.650 --> 02:29.200
Awak nampak seperti zombi.

02:29.810 --> 02:30.470
Yakah?

02:30.870 --> 02:31.690
Taklah.

02:39.710 --> 02:40.310
Hebat.

02:40.329 --> 02:41.110
Agak bagus.

02:46.620 --> 02:47.630
Saya tak boleh tahan lagi.

02:47.710 --> 02:48.590
Saya benar-benar tak boleh tahan lagi.

02:48.590 --> 02:49.450
