02:53.310 --> 02:53.790
Kenapa?

02:53.790 --> 02:54.410
Pelajar.

02:54.470 --> 02:54.950
Pelajar.

02:55.030 --> 02:56.310
Tak boleh duduk segera selepas lari jarak jauh.

02:56.350 --> 02:57.200
